com.tractrac.model.lib.api.metadata

Interface IMetadata


  • public interface IMetadata

    This class represents the metadata associated to an object. In terms of database, metadata is a free text field that can be used by the event administrator in order to extend the system with custom properties.

    The metadata can be structured like a key-value list, a xml, a html... depending on the system administrator. This class contains methods to manage some of these structures.

    Author:
    Jorge Piera Llodrá
